'''''Star Wars Insider'' 36''' is the thirty-sixth issue of ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine, published in [[January]] [[1998]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"The Editor's Desk" {{C|by Jon Bradley Snyder}}
*"[[Rebel Rumblings]]"
*"[[Prequel Update]] with [[Rick McCallum]]" {{C|by Dan Madsen}}
*"[[Star News]]"
*"[[Prequel Profile]]: Robin Gurland" {{C|by [[Pamela Roller]]}}
*"[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe: Phil Brown]]" {{C|by [[Scott Chernoff]]}}
*"[[The Wonder Column|The New Wonder Column]]" {{C|by [[Anthony Daniels]]}}
*"[[The Jawa Trader|Jawa Trader]]"
*"[[The Horse's Mouth|Straight from the Horse's Mouth]]" &ndash; ''Crimson Empire'' {{C|by [[Bob Cooper]]}}
*"[[Scouting the Galaxy]]" {{C|by [[Stephen J. Sansweet]]}}

===Features===
*"[[Liam Neeson: Jedi Master]]" {{C|by [[Lynne Hale]]}}
*:<small>[[Lynne Hale]] has an exclusive interview with the Irish actor who will star in ''Star Wars'': Episode I.</small>
*"[[The Unseen Planets of Star Wars|The Unseen Planets of ''Star Wars'']]" {{C|by [[Daniel Wallace]] with illustrations by [[Chris Trevas]]}}
*:<small>What the heck is [[Ord Mantell/Legends|Ord Mantell]]? Dan Wallace reveals all.</small>
*"[[The Hand of Zahn]]" {{C|by [[Melissa J. Perenson]]}}
*:<small>Beloved ''Star Wars'' author [[Timothy Zahn]] speaks with the Insider's [[Melissa J. Perenson]]</small>
*"[[Be the Jedi in Three New LucasArts Games]]" {{C|by [[Jack Lyon]]}}
*:<small>[[Jack Lyon]] explains how you can be the Jedi in three new ''Star Wars'' games</small>

